      <title>维韦克·拉马斯瓦米希望将国防开支转向新技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ramaswamy-argues-to-shift-defense-spending-toward-new-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与埃隆·马斯克一起被任命削减浪费性开支的前总统候选人维韦克·拉马斯瓦米表示，第二届特朗普政府应该将五角大楼的投资转向无人机和高超音速导弹等新兴技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ramaswamy-argues-to-shift-defense-spending-toward-new-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 21:58:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
