    <item>
      <title>国防部长谴责赫格塞斯对女性参战角色的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/defense-chief-rebukes-hegseth-s-stance-on-women-in-combat-roles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀斥责他的潜在继任者反对女性参与战斗，称这种做法是错误的，会破坏数十年的进步，而且适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/defense-chief-rebukes-hegseth-s-stance-on-women-in-combat-roles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 21:24:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美俄军事首脑一年多来首次通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/us-russian-military-chiefs-speak-for-first-time-in-over-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参谋长联席会议主席与俄罗斯外长一年多来首次通话，讨论乌克兰问题及其他问题，因两国紧张局势持续升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/us-russian-military-chiefs-speak-for-first-time-in-over-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 20:59:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔期望与特朗普政府保持良好关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/powell-says-he-expects-good-relations-with-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔淡化了与即将上任的特朗普政府出现紧张关系的可能性，并表示预计官员们在继续降低利率的同时会谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/powell-says-he-expects-good-relations-with-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 19:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织内部监管机构批评其对巨额贷款的处理方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，国际货币基金组织的内部监管机构批评了该银行向阿根廷和埃及等陷入困境的借款人发放异常巨额贷款的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友批评延长联邦工作人员混合工作制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-allies-blast-work-from-home-extension-for-federal-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的盟友批评了一项将部分联邦工作人员的混合工作选择延长至 2029 年的协议，称社会保障局与其工会之间的协议破坏了重返办公室的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-allies-blast-work-from-home-extension-for-federal-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皮特·赫格塞斯 (Pete Hegseth) 防守机会越来越小，现在取决于恩斯特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hegseth-s-narrowing-chances-for-defense-post-now-turn-on-ernst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的国防部长候选人皮特·赫格塞斯周三与退伍军人共和党参议员乔尼·恩斯特会面时，可能面临了迄今为止他在国会山遇到的最严厉的质询。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hegseth-s-narrowing-chances-for-defense-post-now-turn-on-ernst</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择前美国证券交易委员会委员阿特金斯接替詹斯勒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-names-paul-atkins-as-sec-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保罗·阿特金斯是当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择领导美国证券交易委员会的人选，他建议对加密货币公司对冲基金实行四年宽松的政策和执法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-names-paul-atkins-as-sec-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
